node.title: Missing woman found in critical condition after 12 days
node.description: A woman who went missing from her home in Sandringham is now in intensive care at Auckland Hospital.
node.content:
["A woman who went missing in the central Auckland suburb of Sandringham earlier this month has been found.", "", "
Inquiries are continuing into Cindy Li's disappearance Photo: Supplied / NZ Police
", "Cindy Li was reported missing on 9 November and was found yesterday at an address near her Tranmere Road home.", "Police say the 70-year-old is in a critical but stable condition in the Intensive Care Unit of Auckland Hospital.", "Police will not say if she has suffered injuries or what they know of what has happened to her while she was missing.", "Enquiries are now underway to determine what has occurred.", "Police are examining a property where Li was found.", "Police have thanked all those who provided information during the extensive search."]
